          <tr><td>Primary Owner</td><td>Assignee</td><td>Accountable owner</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="note">What <strong>not to keep</strong> as a GitHub field: Capacity, Derived Hours, FTE, signature state &rarr; belong to the evidence layer.</div>
    </div>

    <h3>9.2 GitHub Actions</h3>
    <div class="card">
